	Liz still in love    
	 London, Sept. 18 (PTI): Their marriage was made in hell.      
	However, actress Elizabeth Taylor, who had twice married and divorced actor Richard Burton, would have tied the knot with him again if he was alive.      
	According to Burtons niece Sian Owen, Taylor considered Burton the love of her life and still keeps a photo of the Welsh actor by her bedside, reports the Daily Mail.      
	I was in America last summer and I went to see Elizabeth. In the house in Bel Air I saw pictures of Uncle Rich everywhere and its a picture of him thats by her bed still, said Owen.    
	Susan strip    
	London (PTI):Actress Susan Sarandons daughter Eva Amurri has turned to stripping in the TV show Californication. The 24-year-old actress stars as Jackie, a student who moonlights in a strip club and yearns for her college professor Hank Moody played by David Duchovny. She peels off a corset to dance for him topless, reports the Daily Mail. She follows the steamy past of her mother who stirred a lot of controversy for a lesbian love scene with Catherine Deneuve in the 1983 film Hunger.     
	Plain nude    
	 New York (PTI): Actress Charlize Theron may have gone nude for the camera many times, but the actress said she is not an exhibitionist. Theron, who has shot naked scenes in her latest film The Burning Plain, said that she only strips off when it is integral to the storyline. Im not some exhibitionist. I think people think I just love walking around naked, she said.                                                                                                                                                                             
